{"tid":711380,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"請教 唔同銀行之間 既存款過戶問題?","createTime":"2018-06-21T13:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T16:06:58.000Z","uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa2cf9bc1899f1a2647d7d0ba784c5e791c2c88","tid":711380,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:05:56.000Z","msg":"例如<br />\n<br />\nhsbc 想過去  中銀戶口<br />\n<br />\n過30萬港紙<br />\n10萬 澳幣<br />\n2萬人仔咁<br />\n<br />\n港紙應該最簡單 係就咁寫支票 我去中銀入番就ok?<br />\n另外d 外幣唔想兌換為港紙 請問係咪 直接另外澳元 人仔 分別寫2張支票 定有咩方法<br />\n<br />\n同埋咁樣會有手續費嗎 <br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒各位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbf8907124f7dde4b86c4e82f20d0f846afde5e","tid":711380,"uid":107470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"人仔可以電子轉帳／支票／chats都得<br />\n本地chats 好似只可以usd hkd cny eur<br />\n如果aud真係要轉既話，就要做電匯，要經中轉行再入收款銀行，會有無兌換手續費同電匯費"},{"pid":"0c7a1873b960cc7d1218770ab7b081b6fc02e026","tid":711380,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"咁直接係hsbc開acc <br />\n再轉錢過去係咪好d 同最簡單?<br />\n<br />\n但開戶應該都搞幾日 唔係即時轉到? thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a34c540dc027600451e54a669be1521c01f3e3","tid":711380,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"無啦啦點解要開個ac轉錢過去？ <br />\n錢係邊度黎？ 轉過去之後打算做咩？"},{"pid":"14ff359833e786fa3cb9b04be6d7826db43f55f2","tid":711380,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c7a1873b960cc7d1218770ab7b081b6fc02e026","tid":711380,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"咁直接係hsbc開acc <br />\n再轉錢過去係咪好d 同最簡單?<br />\n<br />\n但開戶應該都搞幾日 唔係即時轉到? thanks<